with formula_189 a small change of formula_153 in the direction, and formula_191 the corresponding rate of change in the probability distribution. Since relative entropy has an absolute minimum 0 for formula_70, i.e. formula_193, it changes only to &quot;second&quot; order in the small parameters formula_194. More formally, as for any minimum, the first derivatives of the divergence vanish

:formula_195

and by the Taylor expansion one has up to second order

:formula_196

where the Hessian matrix of the divergence

